casebody.data:
Wednesday, March 8, 1989

JURISDICTIONAL MOTIONS ALLOWED

88-2014. Swander Ditch Landowners Assn. v. Joint Bd. of Cty. Commrs.

Huron County, No. H-87-35. On motion to certify, cross-motion to certify, and motion to dismiss. Motion and cross-motion to certify allowed. Motion to dismiss overruled,

Holmes, Wright and H. Brown, JJ., dissent. John W. McCormac, J., of the Tenth Appellate District, sitting for Resnick, J.
